headline: Reassessing Seagate Technology Holdings (STX) After Its 226% One Year Share Price Surge
summary: If you are asking yourself whether Seagate Technology Holdings at US$346.53 still makes sense on a value basis after such a strong run, you are not alone. The stock has delivered returns of 8.2% over the last 7 days, 22.5% over the past month, 20.5% year to date and 225.8% over the last year, with very large gains over 3 and 5 years as well.
